It is now easier to communicate with those friends that don t speak the same language as you. On you chat screen tap their profile pic at the top right and you will see the new option. Flip it ON and when your friend messages you if it s in a different language than your Native Language it will translate it to your Native Language on the left side of the screen. The right side can still be used for translations in to the language you are trying to learn or better develop. When opening a conversation that has new messages waiting for you you can now quickly see which are new because the line to the let will be bolder. To receive Updates automatically go to iTunes App Store in your iPhone settings and switch ON Updates.

English Spanish French German Japanese Korean Chinese Simplified Portuguese Turkish ..more languages to use Neural Machine Translation magic soon.
